Here I will showcase two innovative mini projects that leverage LangChain and ChatGPT to redefine how businesses analyze customer feedback and adapt research insights for varied audiences. The following 2 mini projects illustrate the transformative power of prompt engineering and highlight its practical applications in real-world scenarios.

- AI-Powered Review Analysis: Build an AI system to analyze customer reviews, perform advanced sentiment analysis, and generate actionable responses.

- Audience-Adaptive Content Transformation: Develop an AI expert using ChatGPT to transform research paper abstracts into tailored formats for specific audiences, enhancing accessibility and impact.

